<item>
    <title>Delphine Dora - L'ineluctable pulsation du temps</title>
    <link>http://usefulalgorithm.github.io/posts/2026-04-30-lineluctablepulsationdutemps-delphinedora.html</link>
    <description><![CDATA[<article>
    <section class="header">
        Posted on April 30, 2026
        
        <br>
        
        Tags: <a title="All pages tagged &#39;2026&#39;." href="/tags/2026.html" rel="tag">2026</a>, <a title="All pages tagged &#39;music&#39;." href="/tags/music.html" rel="tag">music</a>, <a title="All pages tagged &#39;modern classical&#39;." href="/tags/modern%20classical.html" rel="tag">modern classical</a>
        
    </section>
    <section>
        <p><img src="https://i.discogs.com/kstPTPjxCj_ax5iOfY-xZI3TVlUfYyBIATsF1bLUeeo/rs:fit/g:sm/q:90/h:600/w:600/czM6Ly9kaXNjb2dz/LWRhdGFiYXNlLWlt/YWdlcy9SLTM2Nzky/NjE2LTE3NzM5MjE2/NzYtODQwNS5qcGVn.jpeg" /></p>
<p>…… 我在想我媽聽理查克萊德門是不是就是這種感覺……</p>
<p>不停重複的鋼琴旋律，逐漸地堆疊、改變著音色。有的時候像音樂盒一樣的叮噹作響，有時又是很太空前衛搖滾那樣的長音。有一天我聽著聽著就在床上睡著，老婆進來叫我的時候說「矮油睡覺還聽這麼好聽的音樂呀。」</p>
<hr />
<p>Fav tracks: Les heures flottantes, La valse du progrès, Désynchronisation, L’inéluctable pulsation du temps</p>
<p>Score: 8.3/10</p>
<p>Release date: 2026-03-13</p>
<p>Labels: Marionette</p>
    </section>
</article>
]]></description>
